1.title: Rally Time

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

1.plot: In a flip from racing semi trucks, Aaron Kaufman takes a stab at building and racing a rally car; Aaron and his builders try to navigate this fast-paced world they know nothing about in which winning is rare for novices and losing can be fatal.

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

2.plot: Aaron and his team need to build and learn to race their Subaru Impreza for the Olympus Rally.

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

3.plot: Aaron and his team struggle just to stay in the game at the Olympus Rally when they're plagued by mishap after mishap.

1.title: A New Start

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

1.plot: Aaron Kaufman sets his sights on an a '71 International Scout to turn it into a street legal Ultra 4 race car for the legendary King of Hammers. Everything about this is new. Hopefully these firsts won't be fails or he'll never make it to King of Hammers.

2.title: Scout 66

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

2.plot: Aaron Kaufman and his team of builders are on the mad dash to get the International Scout ready in time for King of the Hammers. But problem after problem, from redoing the fenders, to leaks, and the car not starting, throws major wrenches into the plan.

3.title: King of the Hammers

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

3.plot: Aaron Kaufman and his team of builders barely make it to King of the Hammers in California, where they will put their '71 International Scout to the ultimate test of rock and desert racing. But can Kaufman's Scout be able to take on the pros?

4.title: Big Rig Gig

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

4.plot: Aaron Kaufman takes on a new challenge to build a Semi-Race Truck. He brings on experts in the field of Semi-Truck racing, Bob Ball and his son Justin to bring the horsepower to the maximum.

5.title: Semi-Charmed Kinda Truck

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

5.plot: The clock is ticking as Aaron Kaufman and his Arclight builders struggle to finish their semi truck in time for race day at Pike's Peak International raceway. Tempers flare and things go wrong. Does this crew have what it takes to make it to the start?

6.title: Trucked and Loaded

episode of.title: Shifting Gears with Aaron Kaufman (TV Series 2018)

6.plot: Aaron Kaufman starts his racing at Pikes Peak International Raceway in Colorado Springs, competing multiple races, and his truck is literally falling apart. Will he be able to finish the event or will he have to be towed back home in pieces?

imdb.plot outline: Aaron Kaufman is back and he's the boss. Redefining the custom car building space, he's pushing his design abilities to the limits and focusing on vehicle builds driven by passion. Taking on concepts and builds he's always dreamed of, Aaron will extend his skills in spaces he's never worked in before and with different types of vehicles in SHIFTING GEARS WITH AARON KAUFMAN.
